source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/chipotle-chicken-rice-bowls-608027a2db13b92aa640e1b2
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: Mexican
author: Sara Heilman
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 630 kcal
